					</div>
									<div id="vers154325" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">2</div>
						<div class="vers-content">He was then sixteen years old, and for fifty years he reigned at Jerusalem; his motherâ€™s name was Jechelia, a woman of Jerusalem.</div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers154326" class="vers">
