						<div class="vers-content">(From Thersa),<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="538">âœ»</a> Menahem brought destruction on Thapsa, and all its inhabitants, and all their country-side, because they would not open the gates to him; ripped up the wombs, too, of the women that were pregnant.<span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
