					</div>
									<div id="vers154348" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">25</div>
						<div class="vers-content">A conspiracy was made against him by one of his own commanders, Phacee son of Romelia, who attacked and slew him in his castle keep (close by Argob and Arie), with fifty Galaadites, and so became king in his place.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="539">âœ»</a></div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers154349" class="vers">
